{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/react/react-element/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Deathdealer's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c1fec2b5-2364-50a9-863d-0365bdb87afe","excerpt":"React 就像一个孩子。在搞清楚这个世界的每一件小事之前，它都要向每一个你所解释的 【X是Y】 询问 【Y是什么】 元素是一个用来描述组件实例或 DOM 节点及其需要属性的普通对象 示例： 翻译成element就是： React 元素可以分为两类： DOM类型的元素 DOM类型的元素使用像h1、div、p等DOM…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>React 就像一个孩子。在搞清楚这个世界的每一件小事之前，它都要向每一个你所解释的 【X是Y】 询问 【Y是什么】</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>元素是一个用来<strong>描述</strong>组件实例或 DOM 节点及其需要属性的普通对象</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\ttype<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>\n  props<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>示例：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>greeting<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Hello, world</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">React.createElement()</code>翻译成element就是：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  type<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"h1\"</span>\n  props<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    className<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"greeting\"</span>\n    children<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello, world\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>React 元素可以分为两类：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>DOM类型的元素</p>\n<p>DOM类型的元素使用像h1、div、p等DOM节点创建React 元素，可以直接渲染的</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>组件类型的元素</p>\n<p>组件类型的元素使用 React 组件创建React元素，需要递归地最终转成DOM类型的元素才能渲染</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>React元素描述的是React虚拟DOM的结构，React会根据虚拟DOM渲染出页面的真实DOM。所有的元素组成的树就是<code class=\"language-text\">element-tree</code></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zh-hans.reactjs.org/blog/2015/12/18/react-components-elements-and-instances.html\">React 组件，元素和实例</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"React Element","date":"2021/08/26 16:07:23","description":"React 就像一个孩子。在搞清楚这个世界的每一件小事之前，它都要向每一个你所解释的 【X是Y】 询问 【Y是什么】"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/react/batched-update/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"如何获取正确的setState之后的值"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/react/children-iteration-methods/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"React Children Utilities"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"c1fec2b5-2364-50a9-863d-0365bdb87afe","previousPostId":"f41ac525-4945-50ec-896c-e2668bc386c0","nextPostId":"4488f158-deb9-53fd-a036-df85780a1f7b"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2355076697","2841359383"]}